page.title: 20New resident to Braceboro'.
page.content: The new resident used to live in Charing Cross in the centre of London.He now lives in Braceborough.He has his own publishing firm in London and he goes to London at least once a week to work.In his spare time he reads and fights in the 'sealed Knot'.An organisation which re-enacts the battles of the civil war.The sides are either cavaliers or roundheads.He is a cavelier.They act the battles of the civil war.The cavaliers have feathers coming out of their hats and wear armour.The cavaliers fight for King Charles whilst the roundheads fight for Oliver Cromwell.He loves living away from London where his little girl can play happily outside.
